version_description: This version is mostly based on this cover from youtube with a few fixes, perhaps look there for strumming pattern. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aOIHXM7WG3I.
Other versions contain incorrect chords and do not include the entirety of the song.
The other version is perfectly fine this just has a few extra chords to make it complete and more like the recording. Also, some of the lyrics were wrong.
